select count(distinct pk1),count(distinct pk2),count(distinct pk3) from t3;
select count(distinct c1),count(distinct c2),count(distinct c3),count(distinct c4),count(distinct c5) from t3;

explain select /*+ index_ss(t3 primary) */ * from t3 where pk3 = 1234;
